# Bonjuçara
[![photo_5136840144136023967_c.jpg](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/ac22a202-547a-4ee0-96b5-5b50858e5ab3/49dc0afc-366e-4037-8b36-477cf17b6e7f/photo_5136840144136023967_c.jpg)](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/ac22a202-547a-4ee0-96b5-5b50858e5ab3/49dc0afc-366e-4037-8b36-477cf17b6e7f/photo_5136840144136023967_c.jpg)

In times of industrialization, intoxication, and mistreatment in handling food; in times of aggressive exploitation of the Earth's most superficial layer to its depths. In times when the sacredness of human relationships perishes, with a loss of meaning, regeneration is necessary.

BonJuçara, "Bon" from Bonete and "Juçara" from the Atlantic Forest, manages, collects, and produces pulp with a "light touch," respecting nature as it deserves and as all healthy food should be treated.

[![IMG_20240926_163651_463.jpg](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/ac22a202-547a-4ee0-96b5-5b50858e5ab3/ced4cec6-e6d9-4255-91d4-8f36e18d7be4/IMG_20240926_163651_463.jpg)](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/ac22a202-547a-4ee0-96b5-5b50858e5ab3/ced4cec6-e6d9-4255-91d4-8f36e18d7be4/IMG_20240926_163651_463.jpg)

[![20240509_113728.jpg](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/ac22a202-547a-4ee0-96b5-5b50858e5ab3/53c7b172-fec0-41f3-ade6-39734e05a9ce/20240509_113728.jpg)](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/ac22a202-547a-4ee0-96b5-5b50858e5ab3/53c7b172-fec0-41f3-ade6-39734e05a9ce/20240509_113728.jpg)

Sustain, nourish, satisfy through taste, prevent and heal, without losing sight of sustainability. For the body that needs prevention and regeneration.

[![20210507_125324.jpg](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/ac22a202-547a-4ee0-96b5-5b50858e5ab3/30f00428-9834-4596-96ee-5ad2173420ea/20210507_125324.jpg)](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/ac22a202-547a-4ee0-96b5-5b50858e5ab3/30f00428-9834-4596-96ee-5ad2173420ea/20210507_125324.jpg)

[![20210507_014226.jpg](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/ac22a202-547a-4ee0-96b5-5b50858e5ab3/5bed6d99-11f3-4a08-b5cf-f78b61a30993/20210507_014226.jpg)](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/ac22a202-547a-4ee0-96b5-5b50858e5ab3/5bed6d99-11f3-4a08-b5cf-f78b61a30993/20210507_014226.jpg)

Juçara, rich in antioxidants and nutrients, is produced by BonJuçara without preservatives or syrups. Therefore, it is carefully preserved at low temperatures. Pure and/or enhanced with other organic fruits from Bonete. Health!

[![20240420_163921-(1).jpg](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/ac22a202-547a-4ee0-96b5-5b50858e5ab3/888ef5ba-f72c-4acd-afdf-d066f2aedf21/20240420_163921-(1).jpg)](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/ac22a202-547a-4ee0-96b5-5b50858e5ab3/888ef5ba-f72c-4acd-afdf-d066f2aedf21/20240420_163921-(1).jpg)

[![20230523_163314.jpg](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/ac22a202-547a-4ee0-96b5-5b50858e5ab3/5309908d-7a93-4e0c-9dad-64b4c1b06481/20230523_163314.jpg)](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/ac22a202-547a-4ee0-96b5-5b50858e5ab3/5309908d-7a93-4e0c-9dad-64b4c1b06481/20230523_163314.jpg)

## **Location** - Praia Grande do Bonete - Ubatuba, SP, Brazil.

[![mapa-local-bonjuçara.jpg](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/5f576b29-86f9-4873-aa25-e05c5c42f339/dc01ec82-90ea-46ed-979f-117f27a78b01/mapa-local-bonjuçara.jpg)](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/5f576b29-86f9-4873-aa25-e05c5c42f339/dc01ec82-90ea-46ed-979f-117f27a78b01/mapa-local-bonjuçara.jpg)

[Google Maps](https://www.google.com.br/maps/dir//-23.5358778,-45.1778639/@-23.5358864,-45.1782689,176m/data=!3m1!1e3?entry=ttu&g_ep=EgoyMDI0MTExNy4wIKXMDSoASAFQAw%3D%3D)

## **Rain and Temperature Chart**: 

[![gráfico-clima.jpg](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/5f576b29-86f9-4873-aa25-e05c5c42f339/7d7431cf-beb4-4bef-a9ea-33c6ccdc04c2/gráfico-clima.jpg)](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/5f576b29-86f9-4873-aa25-e05c5c42f339/7d7431cf-beb4-4bef-a9ea-33c6ccdc04c2/gráfico-clima.jpg)

**Objectives:** 

- Protect the Atlantic Forest, hence we visit and manage it;

- Preserve Juçara from extractivists by cultivating the Juçara palm, managing, processing its fruits, and sowing seeds;

- Reforest previously exploited areas and those affected by criminal fires in 2019;

- Value the Caiçara culture through the production of Juçara pulp, a tradition in some local families;

- Offer consistent job opportunities beyond the domestic service roles provided by local tourism;

- Provide income-generating means to the socially vulnerable community as a way to value, empower, and enable them to continue living in their territory if they choose;

- Provide the children of young Caiçaras with a healthy family farming environment;

- Ensure the "good care" from the hands that harvest to the hands that receive the food.

**GOALS**

- Remove the Juçara palm from the risk of extinction;

- Ensure healthy specimens;

- Monitor and record visits to the forest with periodic vigils;

- Create a record bank for monitoring;

- Equip and train to include native Caiçaras;

- Formalize the cultivation of Juçara as family agriculture through documentation and resources;

- Participate in fairs and events;


[![photo_5136840144136023967_c.jpg](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/ac22a202-547a-4ee0-96b5-5b50858e5ab3/49dc0afc-366e-4037-8b36-477cf17b6e7f/photo_5136840144136023967_c.jpg)](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/ac22a202-547a-4ee0-96b5-5b50858e5ab3/49dc0afc-366e-4037-8b36-477cf17b6e7f/photo_5136840144136023967_c.jpg)

# Bonjuçara

Em tempos de industrialização, intoxicação e maus tratos no lidar com os alimentos; em tempos de exploração  agressiva da camada mais superficial da pele do planeta terra, às suas profundezas. Em tempos que o sagrado das relações humanas perecem, com perda de sentidos, há que se regenerar. 


A BonJuçara, Bon de Bonete e Juçara da Mata Atlântica, maneja, coleta e produz a polpa à "mãos leves", com respeito que a natureza merece e todo alimento para ser saudável deve receber.  

[![IMG_20240926_163651_463.jpg](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/ac22a202-547a-4ee0-96b5-5b50858e5ab3/ced4cec6-e6d9-4255-91d4-8f36e18d7be4/IMG_20240926_163651_463.jpg)](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/ac22a202-547a-4ee0-96b5-5b50858e5ab3/ced4cec6-e6d9-4255-91d4-8f36e18d7be4/IMG_20240926_163651_463.jpg)

[![20240509_113728.jpg](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/ac22a202-547a-4ee0-96b5-5b50858e5ab3/53c7b172-fec0-41f3-ade6-39734e05a9ce/20240509_113728.jpg)](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/ac22a202-547a-4ee0-96b5-5b50858e5ab3/53c7b172-fec0-41f3-ade6-39734e05a9ce/20240509_113728.jpg)

Sustentar, alimentar, satisfazer no degustar, prevenir e curar, sem perder de vista a sustentabilidade. Ao corpo que carece de prevenção e regeneração. 


[![20210507_125324.jpg](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/ac22a202-547a-4ee0-96b5-5b50858e5ab3/30f00428-9834-4596-96ee-5ad2173420ea/20210507_125324.jpg)](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/ac22a202-547a-4ee0-96b5-5b50858e5ab3/30f00428-9834-4596-96ee-5ad2173420ea/20210507_125324.jpg)

[![20210507_014226.jpg](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/ac22a202-547a-4ee0-96b5-5b50858e5ab3/5bed6d99-11f3-4a08-b5cf-f78b61a30993/20210507_014226.jpg)](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/ac22a202-547a-4ee0-96b5-5b50858e5ab3/5bed6d99-11f3-4a08-b5cf-f78b61a30993/20210507_014226.jpg)

A, juçara, rica em antioxidantes e nutrientes, é produzida pela Bonjuçara sem conservantes ou xaropes. Por isto, bem cuidada em baixas temperaturas. Pura e/ou beneficiada com outras frutas orgânicas do Bonete. Saúde!

[![20240420_163921-(1).jpg](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/ac22a202-547a-4ee0-96b5-5b50858e5ab3/888ef5ba-f72c-4acd-afdf-d066f2aedf21/20240420_163921-(1).jpg)](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/ac22a202-547a-4ee0-96b5-5b50858e5ab3/888ef5ba-f72c-4acd-afdf-d066f2aedf21/20240420_163921-(1).jpg)

[![20230523_163314.jpg](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/ac22a202-547a-4ee0-96b5-5b50858e5ab3/5309908d-7a93-4e0c-9dad-64b4c1b06481/20230523_163314.jpg)](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/ac22a202-547a-4ee0-96b5-5b50858e5ab3/5309908d-7a93-4e0c-9dad-64b4c1b06481/20230523_163314.jpg)


## **Local** Praia Grande do Bonete - Ubatuba, SP, Brasil.

[![mapa-local-bonjuçara.jpg](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/5f576b29-86f9-4873-aa25-e05c5c42f339/dc01ec82-90ea-46ed-979f-117f27a78b01/mapa-local-bonjuçara.jpg)](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/5f576b29-86f9-4873-aa25-e05c5c42f339/dc01ec82-90ea-46ed-979f-117f27a78b01/mapa-local-bonjuçara.jpg)


[Google Maps](https://www.google.com.br/maps/dir//-23.5358778,-45.1778639/@-23.5358864,-45.1782689,176m/data=!3m1!1e3?entry=ttu&g_ep=EgoyMDI0MTExNy4wIKXMDSoASAFQAw%3D%3D)

## **Gráfico de chuvas e temperaturas**: 

[![gráfico-clima.jpg](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/5f576b29-86f9-4873-aa25-e05c5c42f339/7d7431cf-beb4-4bef-a9ea-33c6ccdc04c2/gráfico-clima.jpg)](https://cdn.charmverse.io/user-content/5f576b29-86f9-4873-aa25-e05c5c42f339/7d7431cf-beb4-4bef-a9ea-33c6ccdc04c2/gráfico-clima.jpg)

**Objetivos:** 

- Proteger  a Mata Atlântica, por isto visitamos e manejamos;

- Preservar a juçara de extrativistas, para isto cultivamos da palmeira juçara; manejados, beneficiados frutos e semeamos. 

- Reflorestar áreas exploradas anteriomente e sofrida com incêndio criminoso, em 2019;

- Valorizar a cultura caiçara, por meio da produção de polpa de juçara, que foi uma tradição em algumas famílias daqui;

- Oferecer outras opções de trabalho de constância, para além de serviçais do trabalho doméstico oferecido pelo turismo local;

- Oferecer meios rentaveis, à comunidade em situação vunerável socialmente, como meio de valorizar, emancipar e permanecer, sendo do seu querer, viver em seu território;

- Proporcionar às crias das jovens caiçaras, o ambiente saudável da agricultura familiar;

- Fornecer cuidados "do bem querer" das mãos quem colhem, às mãos quem recebem o alimento.



**METAS**

- Tirar a palmeira do risco se extinção; 

- Garantir exemplares saudáveis; 

- Acompanhar e registrar as visitas na Mata com vigílias periódicas; 

- Criar um banco de registros de acompanhamento; 

- Instrumentalizar e formar para incluir nativas caiçaras; 

- Oficializar com documentação e recursos,  o cultivo de juçara como agricultura familiar; 

- Participar de feiras e eventos;

