**_ENTRELINHA CAFÉ - LOURO_**: entrelinha entre as Linhas 1 e 2 de árvores, localizadas no lado do moinho de pedra. A entrelinha possui 7,0 m de largura por 30,0 m de comprimento;

**__COFFEE - LAUREL INTERLINE__**: _interline between Rows 1 and 2 of trees, located on the side of the stone mill. The interline is 7.0 m wide by 30.0 m long;_

