**__Soil preparation__**: _prune the trees in Linhão 1 and 2; create 4 beds (0.60 m X 13.0 m), leaving 0.70 m between beds and 1.50 m between the beds and the tree lines; place coarsely shredded branches between the beds and straw (to prevent soil compaction due to trampling and to maintain a good soil temperature); fertilize the bed with cattle manure (1.9 kg/m²) and cover the bed with shredded branches and straw_;

