**__Planting__**: 31 coffee seedlings in the central planting line (1.0 m between plants) + 15 baleeira seedlings in the right lateral planting line (2.0 m between plants) + 15 baleeira seedlings in the left lateral planting line (2.0 m between plants) + sorrel seeds between the coffee seedlings in the central planting line (1.0 m between plants and two seeds per nest); rice (seed) + sesame (seed) in the lateral lines (left and right) of the baleeira seedlings.

