**__Planting__**: _31 coffee seedlings in the central planting line (1.0 m between plants); sorrel seeds between the coffee seedlings in the central planting line (1.0 m between plants and two seeds per nest); rice (seed) + sesame (seed) + corn in the lateral lines (left and right_).

